{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>A whirlwind of emotions, rampaging spirits, and a topsy-turvy world. Will you be able to save it all? </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><i>MONOWAVE</i></strong> is a puzzle adventure game following the journey of <strong><i>Mono</i></strong>, a newborn Guardian destined to protect the four Emotions: <strong>Anger, Anxiety, Happiness,</strong> and <strong>Sorrow</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">For as long as one can remember, the four Emotions were guided and nurtured by the first Guardian. Everything changed, however, when a blight swept across the land. The first Guardian sacrificed themselves, and the Emotions scattered. It\u2019s up to the new Guardian, Mono, to reunite them once more\u2026</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2680440/extras/intro_1.jpg?t=1738841270\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play as Mono, and use the empathetic powers bestowed upon you to navigate a broken world, one emotion at a time. Soothe the rampage of the isolated Emotions before they cause even more destruction. All straightforward enough\u2026and yet, it seems there\u2019s more to why your new wards are acting out.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2680440/extras/intro_2.jpg?t=1738841270\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2680440/extras/line_happiness.png?t=1738841270\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>4 Unique Emotions &amp; Powers</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">  As the next guardian spirit of the Emotions, you\u2019ll be able to harness special powers based on four emotions: anxiety, anger, sorrow, and happiness. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2680440/extras/emotions.gif?t=1738841270\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Happiness</strong>: Jump to reach new heights. Nothing can stop your glee!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Sorrow</strong>: Dive underwater and flow through narrow passageways to reach unexplored depths.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Anger</strong>: Wall-jump with the power of your fury to pave a path forward.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Anxiety</strong>: Evade potential threats and navigate difficult terrain with your heightened senses.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2680440/extras/line_sorrow.png?t=1738841270\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>A Heartfelt Journey of Empathy</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Our emotions may be turbulent and unpredictable, but they are ultimately what make us human. Uncover a heartfelt story about the complicated but meaningful ways different emotions manifest in our lives.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2680440/extras/absorb_singing.gif?t=1738841270\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2680440/extras/line_anger.png?t=1738841270\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Colorful Cast of Characters</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Because it\u2019s all about the friends we make along the way. Interact with the eccentric inhabitants of each world you explore. Your powers will resonate with them and affect their behaviors. Will they be friend, or foe? It all depends on your approach\u2026</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2680440/extras/friends.gif?t=1738841270\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2680440/extras/line_anxiety.png?t=1738841270\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Four Unique Worlds</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Traverse four unique realms, each warped by the fierce might of its ruling Emotion. From foggy jungles to blazing caverns \u2014 you can uncover them all!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2680440/extras/W1.gif?t=1738841270\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2680440/extras/line_happiness.png?t=1738841270\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>A Whimsical Art Style</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">With a graphics style reminiscent of scratch art from your childhood, MONOWAVE weaves a visual fairytale.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2680440/extras/W1_2.gif?t=1738841270\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2680440/extras/line_sorrow.png?t=1738841270\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Original Soundtrack</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The world of MONOWAVE is brought to life with an all-original, exclusive soundtrack.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2680440/extras/W2.gif?t=1738841270\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2680440/extras/line_anger.png?t=1738841270\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Controller Support</strong></h2>","background":"https://store.akamai.st